title: id
tooltip: This field is unused

title: grade
tooltip: Grade

title: pay date
tooltip: Marks the point for calculating length of service, same as Pay Entry Base Date (PEBD)

title: years service
tooltip: Years of creditable service

title: ets
tooltip: Expiration Term of Service, same as Expiration of Active Obligated Service (EAOS)

title: branch
tooltip: Branch

title: adsn
tooltip: Disbursing Station Symbol Number, identifies each disbursing/finance office

title: period
tooltip: Month covered

title: entitlements
tooltip: Entitlements and allowances being paid. Space is allocated for fifteen line items, if more are present they will be printed in the remarks section. Any retroactive entitlements/allowances will be added to like entitlements/allowances.

title: deductions
tooltip: Deductions being automatically taken. Space is allocated for fifteen line items, if more are present they will be printed in the remarks section. Any retroactive deductions will be added to like deductions.

title: allotments
tooltip: Allotments being automatically taken. Space is allocated for fifteen line items, if more are present they will be printed in the remarks section. If a member has more than one of the same type of allotment, the only differentiation may be that of the dollar amount.

title: amount forward
tooltip: Amount of all unpaid entitlements and allowances due from the prior LES

title: total entitlement
tooltip: Total entitlements/allowances

title: total deduction
tooltip: Total deductions

title: total allotment
tooltip: Total allotments

title: net amount
tooltip: Total of all unpaid entitlements/allowances, plus total entitlements/allowances, minus deductions and allotments due on the current LES

title: carry forward
tooltip: Total of all unpaid entitlements/allowances due to reflect on the next LES as the +AMT FWD

title: end of month pay
tooltip: Actual amount paid to the member at the end of the month

title: diems
tooltip: Date Initially Entered Military Service, used to calculate which retirement plan a member falls under

title: retirement plan
tooltip: Type of retirement plan

title: federal taxes
tooltip: Federal taxes and Federal Income Tax Withholding (FITW)

title: federal taxes wage period
tooltip: Pay earned subject to FITW

title: federal taxes wage ytd
tooltip: Pay earned year-to-date that is subject to FITW

title: federal taxes filing status
tooltip: Federal taxes filing status (married, single, head of household), used to compute FITW bracket

title: multiple jobs
tooltip: Indicator if member has multiple jobs

title: dependents under 17
tooltip: Number of dependents member has under 17 years old

title: other dependents
tooltip: Number of other dependents member has

title: additional tax
tooltip: Member specified dollar amount to be withheld in addition to the amount computed by marital status and exemptions

title: other deductions
tooltip: Total of other miscellaneous deductions

title: other income
tooltip: Total of other income member recieves if they have multiple jobs

title: federal taxes ytd
tooltip: Total of FITW taxes withheld throughout the calendar year

title: fica taxes
tooltip: Federal Insurance Contributions Act taxes

title: fica taxes wage period
tooltip: Pay earned subject to FICA

title: social security wage ytd
tooltip: Pay earned year to date subject to FICA - Social Security

title: social security tax ytd
tooltip: Total of FICA - Social Security taxes withheld throughout the calendar year

title: medicare wage ytd
tooltip: Pay earned year-to-date subject to FICA - Medicare

title: medicare tax ytd
tooltip: Total of FICA - Medicare taxes withheld throughout the calendar year

title: state taxes
tooltip: State taxes and State Income Tax Withholding (SITW)

title: state
tooltip: State used to compute tax residency

title: state taxes wage period
tooltip: Pay earned subject to state taxes

title: state taxes wage ytd
tooltip: Total of state taxes withheld throughout the calendar year

title: state taxes filing status
tooltip: State taxes filing status (married, single), used to compute SITW

title: state taxes exemptions
tooltip: Number of exemptions used to compute SITW

title: state taxes ytd
tooltip: Total of SITW taxes withheld throughout the calendar year

title: pay data
tooltip: Pay data

title: baq type
tooltip: Basic Allowance for Quarters (BAQ) type

title: baq dependents
tooltip: Code indiciating type of dependent (A - Spouse, C - Child, D - Parent, G - Grandfathered, I - Member married to member/own right, K - Ward of  the court, L - Parents in Law, R - Own right, S - Student (age 21-22), T - Handicapped child over age 21, W - Member married to member, child under 21

title: zip code
tooltip: Zip code, used to calculate Variable Housing Allowance (VHA)

title: rent amount
tooltip: Amount of rent paid for housing, if applicable

title: share of rent
tooltip: Number of people which member shares housing costs, if applicable

title: vha status
tooltip: VHA status (accompanied or unaccompanied)

title: jftr
tooltip: Joint Federal Travel Regulation (JFTR) code based on location of member to calculate Cost of Living Allowance (COLA)

title: dependents for jftr
tooltip: Number of dependents member has to calculate VHA

title: jftr 2
tooltip: JFTR code based on the location of the members dependents to calculate COLA

title: bas type
tooltip: Basic Allowance of Subsistence (BAS) type, if applicable. B - Separate rations, C - TDY/PCS/Proceed time, H - Rations-in-kind not available, K - Rations under emergency conditions. This field is blank for officers

title: charity ytd
tooltip: Total amount of charitable contributions throughout the calendar year

title: tpc
tooltip: This field is unused

title: pacidn
tooltip: Unit Identification Code (UIC). Army use only

title: traditional tsp
tooltip: Traditional Thrift Savings Plan (TSP)

title: traditional base pay rate
tooltip: Percentage of base pay elected for traditional TSP contribution

title: traditional base pay current
tooltip: This field is unused

title: traditional special pay rate
tooltip: Percentage of specialty pay elected for traditional TSP contribution

title: traditional special pay current
tooltip: This field is unused

title: traditional incentive pay rate
tooltip: Percentage of incentive pay elected for traditional TSP contribution

title: traditional incentive pay current
tooltip: This field is unused

title: traditional bonus pay rate
tooltip: Percentage of bonus pay elected for traditional TSP contribution

title: traditional bonus pay current
tooltip: This field is unused

title: roth tsp
tooltip: Roth Thrift Savings Plan (TSP)

title: roth base pay rate
tooltip: Percentage of base pay elected for roth TSP contributions

title: roth base pay current
tooltip: This field is unused

title: roth special pay rate
tooltip: Percentage of specialty pay elected for roth TSP contribution

title: roth special pay current
tooltip: This field is unused

title: roth incentive pay rate
tooltip: Percentage of incentive pay elected for roth TSP contribution

title: roth incentive pay current
tooltip: This field is unused

title: roth bonus pay rate
tooltip: Percentage of bonus pay elected for roth TSP contribution

title: roth bonus pay current
tooltip: This field is unused

title: contributions total
tooltip: Contributions total

title: ytd deductions
tooltip: Amount of YTD TSP contributions (combined Traditional and Roth)

title: ytd tsp deferred
tooltip: Amount of YTD TSP contributions deferred for tax purposes. Typically same as total Traditional TSP contributions unless contributions were made in a combat zone

title: ytd tsp exempt
tooltip: Amount of YTD TSP contributions that tax exempt. TSP contributions (whether Traditional or Roth) made in a combat zone are tax-exempt

title: ytd roth
tooltip: Amount of YTD TSP contributions post-tax. Typically same as total Roth TSP contributions unless contributions were made in a combat zone

title: ytd tsp agency auto
tooltip: Total YTD auto contributions (1%) made by the member's contributing agency.

title: ytd tsp agency match
tooltip: Total YTD matched contributions (additional 1%-4%) made by the member's contributing agency. Additional percentage depends on base pay rate.

title: cm agency contribution
tooltip: Contributing agency

title: cm agency auto
tooltip: Monthly auto contributions (1%) made by the member's contributing agency

title: cm agency match
tooltip: Monthly matched contributions (additional 1%-4%) made by the member's contributing agency. Additional percentage depends on base pay rate.

title: leave
tooltip: Leave

title: leave initial balance
tooltip: Brought forward leave balance. Balance may be at the beginning of the fiscal year, when active duty for the member began, or the day after the member was paid a Lump Sum Leave (LSL)

title: leave earned
tooltip: Cumulative amount of leave earned in the current fiscal year or current term of enlistement if the member reenlisted/extended since the beginning of the fiscal year. Normally increases by 2.5 days each month

title: leave used
tooltip: Amount of leave used in the current fiscal year or current term of enlistement if member reenlisted/extended since the beginning of the fiscal year

title: leave current balance
tooltip: Current leave balance at the end of the LES period

title: leave ets balance
tooltip: Projected leave balance to the member's Expiration Term of Service (ETS)

title: leave lost
tooltip: Amount of leave days that have been lost

title: leave paid
tooltip: Amount of leave days that have been paid

title: leave use lose
tooltip: Projected number of days of leave that will be lost if the member does not take them in the current fiscal year on a monthly basis. The number of days in this block will decrease with any leave usage

title: remarks
tooltip: This area is used to provide general notices
